{"tid":2084751,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"KOKO HILLS已獲批預售樓花同意書","createTime":"2020-06-29T12:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T06:24:18.000Z","uid":360878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5074159557f0eca10aec6fe65dd38b64d9ca029","tid":2084751,"uid":360878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"會德豐地產常務董事黃光耀表示，旗下茶果嶺KOKO HILLS已獲批預售樓花同意書，希望24小時內將樓書上網，本周可望開價及開放示範單位，相信項目可成為下半年頭炮新盤<br />\n<br />\n該公司總經理(業務拓展)楊偉銘透露，KOKO HILLS提供413伙，實用面積介乎345至2,024方呎。378伙標準戶中，一房戶面積由366至370方呎，兩房戶面積介乎444至522方呎，三房戶則由546至899方呎。而四房戶面積為1,300方呎。該公司市務助理總經理陳惠慈稱，今期由第2、3及5座組成樓盤主打兩、三房戶佔約八成。項目之後仍有第2、3期發展。"},{"pid":"ed59061be3684e309f9734f5fede660b3e934bac","tid":2084751,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"好似無人討論, 因為未出價單?"},{"pid":"fb8b7241ca7c4837047d3790dd5ef9b775fcc136","tid":2084751,"uid":360878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZTkX28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZTkX28.png&h=968a2994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93f6669b7abccd747a51d305606eea5283891253","tid":2084751,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb8b7241ca7c4837047d3790dd5ef9b775fcc136","tid":2084751,"uid":360878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZTkX28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZTkX28.png&h=968a2994&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"對同區換樓客好吸引"},{"pid":"76b247ba40694516f31019e010fa137707075991","tid":2084751,"uid":360878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"Kokohill 資訊台<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEoq1NquTgyvJQRFfg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEoq1NquTgyvJ